{"tid":838100,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"嘻!C朗同祖記繼續全勝!","createTime":"2018-09-27T00:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T10:35:57.000Z","uid":173952,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c842bcfdf79be5f39eee495bbad2dde3f15de4e8","tid":838100,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:49:08.000Z","msg":"歐洲得番1隊全勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a5420017232858b08cde28460e8c88d789faad","tid":838100,"uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:53:23.000Z","msg":"，意甲第6輪開始6場較量，祖雲達斯主場2比0輕取博洛尼亞，聯賽與歐冠盃7連勝，<span style=\"color: red;\">繼1930-31賽季後第2次賽季開局7連勝</span>。戴巴拿首開紀錄，打破5月以來492分鐘意甲入球荒。C.朗拿度助攻馬杜迪擴大比數，今季意甲已參與5球（3球，2次助攻）。"},{"pid":"9d0327ec1ed59fad5d5df7a1f8aa9de58c02af00","tid":838100,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:56:07.000Z","msg":"朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4acaee738d4ffcdcfda6d7aec57f126a1acb104","tid":838100,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T00:58:08.000Z","msg":"朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88f64522da6552fdf0ce48137b2b9cb8a5d00d3","tid":838100,"uid":155902,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"仲要幫埋大巴拿開齋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇下之前另一邊廂阿根廷果到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3d9b97bef2e5a223b19db7bf7debab27bf6275","tid":838100,"uid":47268,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:12:27.000Z","msg":"意甲都好比<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去養生咋"},{"pid":"ad41f53